imdb.plot outline: Our host Chris Stefanick introduces you to a faith filled group of men and women who know God with certainty, on the basis of His works. Each week, Stefanick assumes the duties of the people he profiles, working alongside crawfish farmers, surfers, hang glider pilots, missionaries to the homeless, miracle historians, and other faith-filled professionals: average folks overcoming loss and embracing the mystery of life. You'll walk away from Real Life Catholic with more than just a glimpse into unfamiliar territory - pilgrimaging to World Youth Day, swimming in cranberries, firing rifles at piñatas and touring through Na Pali by helicopter, for example. If you're like us, you'll end up grasping a new appreciation for how faith works beyond our own natural capacity. Don't take our word for it; see it for yourself. Join Chris as he meets some Real Life Catholics.
imdb.title: Real Life Catholic
plot: Welcome to _Real Life Catholic_ (qv), a new series that dives into everyday life with everyday people: working, serving, building, exploring, and showing how amazing faith makes LIFE.

Our host Chris Stefanick introduces you to a faith filled group of men and women who know God with certainty, on the basis of His works. Each week, Stefanick assumes the duties of the people he profiles, working alongside crawfish farmers, surfers, hang glider pilots, missionaries to the homeless, miracle historians, and other faith-filled professionals: average folks overcoming loss and embracing the mystery of life. You'll walk away from _Real Life Catholic_ (qv) with more than just a glimpse into unfamiliar territory - pilgrimaging to World Youth Day, swimming in cranberries, firing rifles at piñatas and touring through Na Pali by helicopter, for example. If you're like us, you'll end up grasping a new appreciation for how faith works beyond our own natural capacity. Don't take our word for it; see it for yourself. Join Chris as he meets some _Real Life Catholic_ (qv)s.
